Seltzer CRM
Installation Instructions

1. fork repo
2. edit crm/config.inc.php to match what you're doing
3. install docker on server
4. setup watchtower to pull ghcr image
5. setup mail forwarding thingy
6. setup db creds
7. run ghcr image
8. You can now log in using "admin" as the username and the password 'pass'. Please change the password.
9. Optionally go to Plans > Import to upload a CSV file of existing members. See https://github.com/elplatt/seltzer/wiki/HOWTO-Import-Plans for more info.
10. Optionally go to Members > Import to upload a CSV file of existing members. See https://github.com/elplatt/seltzer/wiki/HOWTO-Import-Members for more info.
